data.description: Lovely Cape Cod 4 BR home at Indian Ridge on the West side of beautiful Perry Lake. All bedrooms have HUGE walk-in closets: extra storage or play area for kids. Recently updated kitchen and bathrooms. Newer windows, doors and vinyl siding. Fantastic landscaping, flower gardens and extra lot on the North side make a beautiful outdoor living space with extra room. Great location, Jeff West schools, close to everything and all lake facilities!
